name: Piled up.
description: If I go back through my old photos today, at least half of them, are meaningless. I'm also the kind of person, with nothing organized, or intend to. Random photos piled up, in random folders. Navigating through them sucks. But I have noticed, I keep goin back and back. For whatever reasons. Fill me up with a senses. That one day I'll fix it up neatly. And for now, leave it as is.
